[16.750764, "o", "$ claude_run Say 'DDx plugin loaded' and list the available /ddx: skills. Be brief.\r\n"]
[27.768066, "o", "\r\n\r\nDDx plugin loaded\r\n\r\nI don't see any `/ddx:` skills available in the current environment. The available skills are:\r\n\r\n- `update-config`\r\n- `keybindings-help`\r\n- `simplify`\r\n- `loop`\r\n- `claude-api`\r\n\r\nNone of these are prefixed with `ddx:`. If you expected a DDx plugin to be registered, it may need to be installed or configured.\r\n\u001b[<u\u001b[?1004l\u001b[?2004l\u001b[?25h\u001b]9;4;0;\u0007\u001b]0;\u0007"]
