[98.932234, "o", "  Create a technical design\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n\r\n"]
[100.93738, "o", "$ claude_run\r\n"]
[141.476716, "o", "Technical design created at `docs/helix/02-design/technical-designs/TD-001-temperature-conversion.md`. It covers:\r\n\r\n- **Single entry point** `bin/convert.js` with `#!/usr/bin/env node` shebang\r\n- **Argument parsing** via `process.argv` вЂ” finds `--to-celsius` or `--to-fahrenheit`, reads the next element as the temperature\r\n- **Two conversion functions** using the PRD formulas, output with `toFixed(1)`\r\n- **Error handling** вЂ” missing flag, missing value, or non-numeric value all print usage to stderr and exit 1\r\n- **File structure** вЂ” just `bin/convert.js` and a `package.json` with a `bin` field\r\n- **Test cases** drawn from the US-001 acceptance criteria\r\n\u001b[<u\u001b[?1004l\u001b[?2004l\u001b[?25h\u001b]9;4;0;\u0007\u001b]0;\u0007"]
[141.633896, "o", "\u001b[?25h"]
[141.713053, "o", "\r\n"]
